<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.json">
    <title>RB TIMED AUCTION</title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
    <meta charset="utf-8"> 
</head>

<body class="body USD">
	<div class="js--tal">
        <!-- @include '/assets/components/layout/header' -->
        
        <div class="l-main-container"> 
            <div class="js--nav-pin-waypoint"></div>
            <div class="l-pin-header-wrapper js--pinned-header">
                <div class="l-pin-header-inner">
                    <div class="l-scroll-revealable-header" v-bind:class="{'s-showWholeHeader' : showSecondaryHeader}">
                        <!-- @include '/assets/components/components/navigation_tabs' -->
                    </div>

                    <div class="c-navigation__tertiary g-wrapper">
                        <div class="g-cell t-h3 t-lh-300 h-color-white t-bold">
                            {{ choiceGroups.length > 1 ? choiceGroups.length + ' Choice Groups' : choiceGroups.length === 1 ? '1 Choice Group' : 'No Choice Groups Created Yet'}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="g-cell h-ta-right">
                            <button class="o-button__tertiary">Create <span class="h-hide-mobile"> a choice group</span><span class="h-hide-desktop"> new</span></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div v-if="choiceGroups.length > 0">
                <!-- @include '/assets/components/components/choice_group-view' -->
                <!-- @include '/assets/components/components/choice_group-view' --> 
            </div>
            <div v-else class="l-container__medium">
                <div class="h-ta-center h-mt-500 h-mb-500">
                    <img src="assets/img/empty.png">
                    <h3 class="t-h3">You haven't created any choice groups yet!</h3>
                    <button class="o-button__primary" v-on:click="gotoPage('index')">Create your first choice group</button>
                </div>
                <div class="o-message__info h-mb-300">
                    <p>In our live auctions, similar items are sometimes sold as choice group. In the Timed Auction, you can create your own choice group. This is a good option if you want to buy a certain type of item, rather than a specific lot. For example, if we're selling 10 identical gen sets and you want to buy three of them, you can create a choice group out of the 10 items and specify that you want a quantity of up to three.</p>
                    <a href="http://www.rbauction.com/buying/how-to-buy/at-a-timed-auction/advanced-bidding" class="t-link__message" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        <!-- @include '/assets/components/layout/footer_paginated' -->
        <footer>Prototype controls: <button v-on:click="emptyGroups">Show Empty Version</button></footer>
	</div>
    <!-- @include '/assets/components/components/js-includes' -->

</body>
</html>